{"tid":966782,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"斷食同節食分別到底係邊","createTime":"2019-01-03T05:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T02:33:23.000Z","uid":126569,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"61fbcc582b03e2fad17db0084f855912e3884285","tid":966782,"uid":126569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9JK_kaYSnQ0&amp;t=727s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9JK_kaYSnQ0%26t%3D727s&d=9M7Xd7PTM5cbQZimQZnUp0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=409c1af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9JK_kaYSnQ0&amp;t=727s</a><br />\n<br />\n討論之前可以睇下上面條片。<br />\n<br />\n我想討論既並唔係間歇性斷食，而係長時間斷食<br />\n<br />\n到底點解長時間斷食就可以保持肌肉量<br />\n<br />\n相反節食就唔得?"},{"pid":"15dda03ba5a90c5b2207aa73613c1227bd22580d","tid":966782,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"個樣有啲似牛佬"},{"pid":"998865a4a2938dbe92190c4b653496d968601d8b","tid":966782,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"點講好<br />\n48小時斷食同節食我都試過<br />\n斷食感覺係清緊體內既垃圾<br />\n同埋後面會好撚精神<br />\n節食係keep住肚餓唔嗲唔吊咁<br />\n同埋無乜精神<br />\n我都唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef12e82334dd04f5fe3676ad7ddd05aa96aa951a","tid":966782,"uid":126569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998865a4a2938dbe92190c4b653496d968601d8b","tid":966782,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"點講好<br />\n48小時斷食同節食我都試過<br />\n斷食感覺係清緊體內既垃圾<br />\n同埋後面會好撚精神<br />\n節食係keep住肚餓唔嗲唔吊咁<br />\n同埋無乜精神<br />\n我都唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"但係兩者都會食唔夠TDEE，點解節食反而會拆多D肌肉"},{"pid":"106b08d5a6d32f59c64ef79fc6d0a9331009f354","tid":966782,"uid":37612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-